{
  "texts": [
    "We adopt different methods to generate the Temporal Exchange and Temporal Description data described in Sec. 3.4.",
    "Yet, both are followed by human (the first 4 authors) checking and correction to ensure the quality.",
    "Specifically, to get the data of Temporal Exchange, we prompt GPT-4 by giving the original question and correct answer pairs.",
    "In our implementation, we find it is better to use different prompts to handle questions about \"before/after\" and questions about \"when/while\".",
    "Specific prompts are presented in Tab. 6."
  ]
}